#: templates/timeline.html.jinja:314
msgid "timeline.tables.subtasks.help_title"
msgstr "How do Subtasks affect Spent Time?"

#: templates/timeline.html.jinja:314
msgid "timeline.tables.subtasks.help_text"
msgstr ""
"YouTrack implicitly adds the <code>Spent Time</code> of each subtask to "
"the total <code>Spent Time</code>. Because of this, it may seem that the "
"task has been delayed, but in fact, time has accumulated in another "
"place altogether. The table below shows each subtask (if any), as well "
"as its <code>Spent Time</code> and percentage of the total."

